H\u00f6ga inmatningsavgifter g\u00f6r att m\u00e5nga solcells\u00e4gare producerar mindre gr\u00f6n el \u00e4n de skulle vilja. Nu f\u00f6resl\u00e5r Energimarknadsinspektionen att avgiften skrotas f\u00f6r mikroproducenter av el.<\/p>\n","category_list":"
{"id":4210,"date":"2021-05-17T13:28:00","date_gmt":"2021-05-17T11:28:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/el.kampanj.etc.se\/nyheter\/nyheter-skrotad-avgift-kan-ge-mer-el-fran-solen-0\/"},"modified":"2022-04-20T18:36:41","modified_gmt":"2022-04-20T16:36:41","slug":"skrotad-avgift-kan-ge-mer-el-fran-solen-0","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/nyheter\/skrotad-avgift-kan-ge-mer-el-fran-solen-0\/","title":{"rendered":"Skrotad avgift kan ge mer el fr\u00e5n solen"},"content":{"rendered":"
H\u00f6ga inmatningsavgifter g\u00f6r att m\u00e5nga solcells\u00e4gare producerar mindre gr\u00f6n el \u00e4n de skulle vilja. Nu f\u00f6resl\u00e5r Energimarknadsinspektionen att avgiften skrotas f\u00f6r mikroproducenter av el.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4211,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[1],"tags":[],"blocksy_meta":{"styles_descriptor":{"styles":{"desktop":"","tablet":"","mobile":""},"google_fonts":[],"version":5}},"featured_image_urls":{"full":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/sdlbwrwci-8na4-nh.jpeg",1600,900,false],"thumbnail":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/sdlbwrwci-8na4-nh-150x150.jpeg",150,150,true],"medium":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/sdlbwrwci-8na4-nh-300x169.jpeg",300,169,true],"medium_large":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/sdlbwrwci-8na4-nh-768x432.jpeg",768,432,true],"large":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/sdlbwrwci-8na4-nh-1024x576.jpeg",1024,576,true],"1536x1536":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/sdlbwrwci-8na4-nh-1536x864.jpeg",1536,864,true],"2048x2048":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/sdlbwrwci-8na4-nh.jpeg",1600,900,false]},"post_excerpt_stackable":"
