Men 11\u201314 procent \u00e4r inte en d\u00e5lig siffra hur som helst.<\/p>\n\n\n\n
En stor del av den solel som produceras g\u00e5r ju till konsumtion direkt i huset som har solcellerna. R\u00e4knar man med att bara 20% av elen anv\u00e4nds direkt s\u00e5 blir det \u00e4nd\u00e5 hela 11,5 procent av v\u00e5r elanv\u00e4ndning denna timme. <\/p>\n\n\n\n
Fortfarande bromsas ju solel med m\u00e4rkliga regler fr\u00e5n n\u00e4tbolagen vad g\u00e4ller inkoppling och med extraskatt f\u00f6r riktigt stora fastigheters anl\u00e4ggningar.<\/p>\n\n\n\n
F\u00f6r f\u00f6rsta g\u00e5ngen gav solel mer \u00e4n 1 Gigawatt inmatat p\u00e5 n\u00e4tet. <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":7324,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[1],"tags":[],"blocksy_meta":{"styles_descriptor":{"styles":{"desktop":"","tablet":"","mobile":""},"google_fonts":[],"version":5}},"featured_image_urls":{"full":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/10\/webb_solel_rekord.jpg",1600,900,false],"thumbnail":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/10\/webb_solel_rekord-150x150.jpg",150,150,true],"medium":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/10\/webb_solel_rekord-300x169.jpg",300,169,true],"medium_large":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/10\/webb_solel_rekord-768x432.jpg",768,432,true],"large":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/10\/webb_solel_rekord-1024x576.jpg",1024,576,true],"1536x1536":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/10\/webb_solel_rekord-1536x864.jpg",1536,864,true],"2048x2048":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/10\/webb_solel_rekord.jpg",1600,900,false]},"post_excerpt_stackable":"
