\u2013 N\u00e4r debatten nu har kommit ut tror vi att den kommer resultera i diskussioner inom de politiska partierna, s\u00e4ger Gudrun Schyman.<\/p>\n
{"id":4153,"date":"2021-10-05T14:22:00","date_gmt":"2021-10-05T12:22:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/el.kampanj.etc.se\/nyheter\/nyheter-de-vill-se-ny-allians-radikal-klimatpolitik\/"},"modified":"2022-04-20T18:33:03","modified_gmt":"2022-04-20T16:33:03","slug":"de-vill-se-ny-allians-radikal-klimatpolitik","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/nyheter\/de-vill-se-ny-allians-radikal-klimatpolitik\/","title":{"rendered":"De vill se ny allians f\u00f6r radikal klimatpolitik"},"content":{"rendered":"
\u2013 Vi \u00e4r ett antal personer med olika bakgrund och \u00adprofessioner som k\u00e4nner att vi beh\u00f6ver samla ihop oss. Den traditionella partipolitiken f\u00f6rm\u00e5r inte hantera det faktum att det m\u00e5ste ske saker nu, s\u00e4ger Gudrun Schyman.<\/p>\n
En grupp ex-politiker, religi\u00f6sa ledare och gr\u00e4sr\u00f6tter krokar arm inf\u00f6r valet 2022.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4154,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[1],"tags":[],"blocksy_meta":{"styles_descriptor":{"styles":{"desktop":"","tablet":"","mobile":""},"google_fonts":[],"version":5}},"featured_image_urls":{"full":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/klimatiniativet.jpeg",1600,900,false],"thumbnail":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/klimatiniativet-150x150.jpeg",150,150,true],"medium":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/klimatiniativet-300x169.jpeg",300,169,true],"medium_large":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/klimatiniativet-768x432.jpeg",768,432,true],"large":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/klimatiniativet-1024x576.jpeg",1024,576,true],"1536x1536":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/klimatiniativet-1536x864.jpeg",1536,864,true],"2048x2048":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/klimatiniativet.jpeg",1600,900,false]},"post_excerpt_stackable":"
Deltagarna vid presskon\u00adferensen lyfte s\u00e4rskilt fram att klimatet har begr\u00e4nsats till en h\u00f6ger-v\u00e4nster-fr\u00e5ga \u2013 n\u00e4r det i sj\u00e4lva verket \u00e4r en existentiell fr\u00e5ga som handlar om liv och d\u00f6d.<\/p>\n
F\u00f6rutom Gudrun Schyman \u00ad(tidigare partiledare f\u00f6r V och FI) h\u00f6r f\u00f6re detta \u00e4rkebiskopen KG Hammar, den pensionerade imamen Awad Olwan och tidigare M- och KD-politikern Anders Wijkman till dem som st\u00e5r bakom den s\u00e5 kallade Klimatalliansen. Det nya initiativet lanserades p\u00e5 en presskonferens i m\u00e5ndags och via en debattartikel i DN under s\u00f6ndagskv\u00e4llen.<\/p>\n
Hur ska ni jobba rent \u00adkonkret f\u00f6r att f\u00e5 genomslag f\u00f6r ert initiativ?<\/p>\n


