SOURCE: https://etcel.se/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/7496
Att s\u00e4lja el fr\u00e5n solceller \u00e4r ett bra s\u00e4tt att tj\u00e4na pengar p\u00e5 din egen produktion av f\u00f6rnybar energi. Genom att installera solceller p\u00e5 taket eller i tr\u00e4dg\u00e5rden kan du b\u00f6rja producera el och s\u00e4lja \u00f6verskottet till elbolaget. Detta \u00e4r en milj\u00f6v\u00e4nlig och l\u00f6nsam investering som kan hj\u00e4lpa dig att minska din elr\u00e4kning och bidra till en mer h\u00e5llbar framtid. L\u00e4s vidare f\u00f6r att l\u00e4ra dig mer om hur du kan s\u00e4lja el fr\u00e5n solceller och vad du beh\u00f6ver t\u00e4nka p\u00e5.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":5420,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[1],"tags":[],"blocksy_meta":{"styles_descriptor":{"styles":{"desktop":"","tablet":"","mobile":""},"google_fonts":[],"version":5}},"featured_image_urls":{"full":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/IMG_20170609_160338133_HDR_1170x.jpeg",1170,658,false],"thumbnail":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/IMG_20170609_160338133_HDR_1170x-150x150.jpeg",150,150,true],"medium":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/IMG_20170609_160338133_HDR_1170x-300x169.jpeg",300,169,true],"medium_large":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/IMG_20170609_160338133_HDR_1170x-768x432.jpeg",768,432,true],"large":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/IMG_20170609_160338133_HDR_1170x-1024x576.jpeg",1024,576,true],"1536x1536":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/IMG_20170609_160338133_HDR_1170x.jpeg",1170,658,false],"2048x2048":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2022\/03\/IMG_20170609_160338133_HDR_1170x.jpeg",1170,658,false]},"post_excerpt_stackable":"
