Passa p\u00e5 att ta en promenad f\u00f6rbi <\/strong>bygget i v\u00e5rsolen. Byggarbetsplatsen \u00e4r inh\u00e4gnad s\u00e5 man kan inte (och f\u00e5r inte) g\u00e5 in som bes\u00f6kare. Men utanf\u00f6r st\u00e4ngslet ser man allt lika bra s\u00e5 vill du se husbygget \u00e4r det bara att \u00e5ka dit.<\/p>\n
Nu g\u00e5r det fort och det h\u00e4nder saker varje dag. H\u00e4r f\u00e5r du den senaste uppdateringen med bilder fr\u00e5n bygget av ETC Hyreshus i V\u00e4ster\u00e5s.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":333,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[5],"tags":[],"blocksy_meta":{"styles_descriptor":{"styles":{"desktop":"","tablet":"","mobile":""},"google_fonts":[],"version":5}},"featured_image_urls":{"full":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2021\/05\/image0-on1.jpg",1962,1472,false],"thumbnail":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2021\/05\/image0-on1-150x150.jpg",150,150,true],"medium":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2021\/05\/image0-on1-300x225.jpg",300,225,true],"medium_large":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2021\/05\/image0-on1-768x576.jpg",768,576,true],"large":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2021\/05\/image0-on1-1024x768.jpg",1024,768,true],"1536x1536":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2021\/05\/image0-on1-1536x1152.jpg",1536,1152,true],"2048x2048":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2021\/05\/image0-on1.jpg",1962,1472,false]},"post_excerpt_stackable":"
Klimat<\/a>","author_info":{"name":"ETC","url":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/author\/itadmin\/"},"comments_num":"0 comments","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/328"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=328"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/328\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":854,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/328\/revisions\/854"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/333"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=328"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=328"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=328"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}
N\u00e4r f\u00f6rsta huset \u00e4r monterat s\u00e5 kommer vi s\u00e4tta ig\u00e5ng med hus nummer tv\u00e5.
Vill du vara med och spara i v\u00e5ra klimatsmarta hyreshus?<\/strong> N\u00e4sta steg \u00e4r V\u00e4xj\u00f6 d\u00e4r vi kommer ta in ytterligare 50 miljoner f\u00f6r att bygga tre nya hus p\u00e5 en g\u00e5ng. Hyreshusen har en avkastning till sparare p\u00e5 2 procent per \u00e5r.<\/p>\n
Du kan l\u00e4sa mer om att spara med ETC h\u00e4r.<\/a>
Nu g\u00e5r det fort och det h\u00e4nder saker varje dag. H\u00e4r f\u00e5r du den senaste uppdateringen med bilder fr\u00e5n bygget av ETC Hyreshus i V\u00e4ster\u00e5s.<\/p>\n
