Energi<\/a>","author_info":{"name":"ETC","url":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/author\/itadmin\/"},"comments_num":"0 comments","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4181"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4181"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4181\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4292,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4181\/revisions\/4292"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4182"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4181"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4181"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4181"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}
Under vandringskonsertens g\u00e5ng f\u00e5r du, ut\u00f6ver insikt i solceller, m\u00f6ta levande flamencolegenden Eva M\u00f6ller som l\u00e4ser utvalda \u00f6vers\u00e4ttningar av flamencoverser ur den nyligen utgivna boken Recital ? rop som g\u00e5r i arv. Vandringen forts\u00e4tter med ett utdrag ur f\u00f6rest\u00e4llningen Carmen Recycled som fick sin premi\u00e4r tidigare i \u00e5r i Scenkonst S\u00f6rmlands produktion, en \u00e5tervunnen upplevelse om makt, k\u00e4rlek och att \u00e4ga r\u00e4tten till sin ber\u00e4ttelse.<\/p>\n


