\/ \u201dBekymrad\u201d<\/em><\/p>\n
\u00c4r det sant att solel produceras med kolel?<\/h5>\n
Varf\u00f6r ligger Sverige i bakvattnet med solceller?<\/h5>\n
L\u00e4sarfr\u00e5ga: <\/strong>N\u00e4r jag l\u00e4ser om solceller i tekniktidningar f\u00e5r jag en k\u00e4nsla av att det h\u00e4nder v\u00e4ldigt mycket hela tiden. \u00c4nd\u00e5 \u00e4r det de \u201dvanliga\u201d kiselsolcellerna bland annat du rekommenderar i din bok. Varf\u00f6r \u00e4r det s\u00e5 att det just inom solceller utvecklas s\u00e5 sakta?<\/p>\n
Energi<\/a>","author_info":{"name":"ETC","url":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/author\/itadmin\/"},"comments_num":"0 comments","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/376"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=376"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/376\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":874,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/376\/revisions\/874"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/206"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=376"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=376"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=376"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}
Sedan \u00e4r det ju ren l\u00f6gn att Stockholm skulle ha ren el. Den st\u00f6rsta klimatf\u00f6rst\u00f6raren i Stockholm \u00e4r V\u00e4rtaverket d\u00e4r man br\u00e4nner f\u00f6r fj\u00e4rrv\u00e4rme och g\u00f6r el. Utsl\u00e4ppen \u00e4r enorma och \u00e4ven fossila. I flera andra st\u00e4der \u00e4r det samma sak, p\u00e5 senare \u00e5r har fj\u00e4rrv\u00e4rmen dessutom storsatsat p\u00e5 att br\u00e4nna sopor, det vill s\u00e4ga plast. Det finns inget klimatrent i den el som d\u00e5 produceras.<\/p>\n
Det \u00e4r n\u00e5gra av svaren fr\u00e5n Johan Ehrenberg, som svarar p\u00e5 fyra l\u00e4sarfr\u00e5gor fr\u00e5n Dagens ETC om solceller.<\/p>\n


