Solel b\u00f6rjar synas i siffrorna nu Ja, det \u00e4r fortfarande sm\u00e5 rekord, men f\u00f6r de som satsar p\u00e5 ren el \u00e4r de f\u00f6rsta stegen kanske de viktigaste.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[4],"tags":[],"blocksy_meta":{"styles_descriptor":{"styles":{"desktop":"","tablet":"","mobile":""},"google_fonts":[],"version":5}},"featured_image_urls":{"full":"","thumbnail":"","medium":"","medium_large":"","large":"","1536x1536":"","2048x2048":""},"post_excerpt_stackable":"
Solelen b\u00f6rjar visa sig \u00e4ven i Sverige!<\/span><\/p>\n
{"id":770,"date":"2015-07-13T00:16:00","date_gmt":"2015-07-12T22:16:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/el.kampanj.etc.se\/nyheter\/solel-till-hela-landet\/"},"modified":"2021-05-17T13:20:40","modified_gmt":"2021-05-17T11:20:40","slug":"solel-till-hela-landet","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/energi\/solel-till-hela-landet\/","title":{"rendered":"Solel till hela landet"},"content":{"rendered":"
F\u00f6rra m\u00e5naden blev b\u00e4sta solcellsm\u00e5naden f\u00f6r ETC el och ETC Elproduktion. F\u00f6r ETC el betyder det att 10,1% av all el som levererades till kunderna kom fr\u00e5n Elproduktions solceller. Det \u00e4r mer \u00e4n n\u00e5got annat elbolag i Sverige. R\u00e4knar man \u201dmitt p\u00e5 dagen tid” s\u00e5 fick ETC els kunder n\u00e4stan 30 procent av sin el fr\u00e5n solelen! P\u00e5 natten \u00e4r det vattenkraft som vi levererar ifr\u00e5n. <\/p>\n
Energi<\/a>","author_info":{"name":"ETC","url":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/author\/itadmin\/"},"comments_num":"0 comments","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/770"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=770"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/770\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1052,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/770\/revisions\/1052"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=770"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=770"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/etcel.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=770"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}
Men egen el d\u00e5. Allts\u00e5 solceller hemma hos m\u00e4nniskor. <\/span>
R\u00e4knar man bara de anl\u00e4ggningar ETC och systerbolaget Egen El sj\u00e4lva satt upp och kan m\u00e4ta s\u00e5 producerade egen els solceller totalt el till ungef\u00e4r 1230 l\u00e4genheter under juni. R\u00e4knat p\u00e5 dagtid s\u00e5 \u00e4r det 3700 l\u00e4genheter runtom i landet.<\/span><\/p>\n
Solel b\u00f6rjar synas i siffrorna nu Ja, det \u00e4r fortfarande sm\u00e5 rekord, men f\u00f6r de som satsar p\u00e5 ren el \u00e4r de f\u00f6rsta stegen kanske de viktigaste. <\/p>\n


