\u2013 Solel g\u00f6r lika mycket klimatnytta i Indien som i Europa. Och utbildning \u00e4r v\u00e4gen fram\u00e5t f\u00f6r oss alla.<\/p>\n
F\u00f6r tredje \u00e5ret i rad har ETC-familjen beslutat att ist\u00e4llet inte ge n\u00e5gra julklappar inom f\u00f6retagen. Ist\u00e4llet ger vi motsvarande summa till daliternas, de \u201dober\u00f6rbaras\u201d, kamp f\u00f6r social r\u00e4ttvisa och en b\u00e4ttre framtid i Indien.  Det \u00e4r en julg\u00e5va som kan f\u00f6r\u00e4ndra vardagslivet f\u00f6r en hel by. Den resulterar n\u00e4mligen varje \u00e5r i en ny skola, som drivs av solceller.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":581,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[4],"tags":[],"blocksy_meta":{"styles_descriptor":{"styles":{"desktop":"","tablet":"","mobile":""},"google_fonts":[],"version":5}},"featured_image_urls":{"full":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2021\/05\/handskakning.png",1600,900,false],"thumbnail":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2021\/05\/handskakning-150x150.png",150,150,true],"medium":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2021\/05\/handskakning-300x169.png",300,169,true],"medium_large":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2021\/05\/handskakning-768x432.png",768,432,true],"large":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2021\/05\/handskakning-1024x576.png",1024,576,true],"1536x1536":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2021\/05\/handskakning-1536x864.png",1536,864,true],"2048x2048":["https:\/\/wordpress.etc.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/10\/2021\/05\/handskakning.png",1600,900,false]},"post_excerpt_stackable":"
